metadata.name: Revive
metadata.description:
Having found its Light within, the Being effortlessly travels across the dead land, reviving it back to life with its sheer presence.

When we live in Pure Presence, there's nothing that can overpower us. By being touch with the core of our Being, we emenate a powerful energy field which is healing for ourselves and others around us.

Animation & Music by Juuso Hämäläinen

Original File Size: 1500x2000 px
